title: KitchenAid 48" Dual Fuel Even Heat True Convection Range - KDRS483VSS
description:
Buy GE KDRS483VSS - http://www.abt.com/product/46837/KitchenAid-KDRS483VSS.html
Shop Ranges - http://www.abt.com/category/459/Dual-Fuel-Ranges.html

Features:
• Dual fuel ranges offer the precision of a gas cooking surface with an electric oven
• Even-Heat™ True Convection System provides consistent heating and even cooking on all three racks
• EasyConvect™ Time and Temperature Conversion System takes the guesswork out of convection cooking
• 5K BTU simmer/melt burner is designed to cook foods gently at lower temperatures
• Large glass-touch oven display features a responsive easy-to-use interface and is easy to clean
• Commercial-style design features a heavy-duty look with robust knobs and a stainless steel handle
• Two 20K BTU Ultra Power™ Dual-Flame Burners offer versatility from intense searing to low simmering
